bosun
=====

The Debian Package bosun
----------------------------

Installs pre-build binary from github repo and minimal config with upstart job

Building
========
Just run ```debuild``` in package directory, it will download binary for the release
mentioned in debian/changelog from github and build a package.

Updating
========
Just run ```make update``` and it will update changelog from the releases page (if you want, you can specify particular release by calling ./build/generate-changelog <tag_name>)
